statements.sql: select `opd`.`id`, `opd`.`nama` from `bidang_permissions` inner join `opd` on `bidang_permissions`.`opd_id` = `opd`.`id` where `bidang_permissions`.`bidang_id` = '1' order by `opd`.`nama` asc

select distinct `program`.`id`, `program`.`nama` from `program` inner join `kegiatan` on `program`.`id` = `kegiatan`.`program_id` inner join `anggaran` on `kegiatan`.`id` = `anggaran`.`kegiatan_id` where `anggaran`.`tahapan_id` = '6' and `anggaran`.`opd_pelaksana_id` = '19' order by `program`.`nama` asc

select count(*) as aggregate from `anggaran` inner join `bidang_permissions` on `anggaran`.`opd_id` = `bidang_permissions`.`opd_id` inner join `kegiatan` on `anggaran`.`kegiatan_id` = `kegiatan`.`id` inner join `tahapan` on `anggaran`.`tahapan_id` = `tahapan`.`id` inner join `program` on `kegiatan`.`program_id` = `program`.`id` where `bidang_permissions`.`bidang_id` = '1' and `anggaran`.`tahapan_id` = '6' and `program`.`id` = '22'

select `anggaran`.`id`, `anggaran`.`is_transfer`, `anggaran`.`lokasi`, `anggaran`.`created_at`, `bidang_permissions`.*, `kegiatan`.`nama`, `anggaran`.`prioritas`, `anggaran`.`is_verifikasi`, `anggaran`.`catatan` from `anggaran` inner join `bidang_permissions` on `anggaran`.`opd_id` = `bidang_permissions`.`opd_id` inner join `kegiatan` on `anggaran`.`kegiatan_id` = `kegiatan`.`id` inner join `tahapan` on `anggaran`.`tahapan_id` = `tahapan`.`id` inner join `program` on `kegiatan`.`program_id` = `program`.`id` where `bidang_permissions`.`bidang_id` = '1' and `anggaran`.`tahapan_id` = '6' and `program`.`id` = '22' order by `anggaran`.`prioritas` asc, `anggaran`.`created_at` asc limit 10 offset 0
